news.message: Earn New Rewards with Nightwave Series 2!

news.message: Valkyr and Saryn Prime Vault Available Now!

translations.fr: Prime Vault de Valkyr Prime et Saryn Prime disponible maintenant!
translations.it: Valkyr e Saryn Prime Disponibili Ora!
translations.de: Valkyr Prime und Saryn Prime Vault jetzt verfügbar!
translations.es: ¡Prime Vault de Valkyr y Saryn ya están disponibles!

translations.fr: Le Prime Access Wukong Prime se termine le 1er octobre!
translations.it: L'Accesso Wukong Prime Terminerà l'1 Ottobre!
translations.de: Wukong Prime Access endet am 1. October!
translations.es: ¡Prime Access de Wukong termina el 1 de octubre!
translations.pt: O Wukong Prime Access terminará no dia 1º de outubro!
translations.ru: Доступ к Вуконг Прайм заканчивается 1 Октября!
